      "versionNonce": 431915464,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770992160097,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "1) Optimising Browse Queries:\n\n- We have 20,000 browsers per day making multiple requests. If these go\nstraight to the same DB as used for purchases this may block purchases.\nWe should separate these concerns and have a read optimised DB for browse\nqueries and a robust, transactional DB for purchases.\n\nStructure the DB as follows:",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "1) Optimising Browse Queries:\n\n- We have 20,000 browsers per day making multiple requests. If these go\nstraight to the same DB as used for purchases this may block purchases.\nWe should separate these concerns and have a read optimised DB for browse\nqueries and a robust, transactional DB for purchases.\n\nStructure the DB as follows:",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
