      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1770992924009,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "/get-product/{productId} - satisfied by partition Key\n/get-all-product - table scan, but paginated to ensure speed\n/get-by-category/{catId} - satisfied by sort key\n\nfilters e.g. on price/color. Local secondary index can be used for the\nmost high traffic alternative sorts. For low traffic, we simply use the filter\nfunction (which is less efficient for reads but costs less in storage and I/O of \nDynamoDB)\n\nGSI can be used for other high traffic queries e.g. /get-by-gender",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "/get-product/{productId} - satisfied by partition Key\n/get-all-product - table scan, but paginated to ensure speed\n/get-by-category/{catId} - satisfied by sort key\n\nfilters e.g. on price/color. Local secondary index can be used for the\nmost high traffic alternative sorts. For low traffic, we simply use the filter\nfunction (which is less efficient for reads but costs less in storage and I/O of \nDynamoDB)\n\nGSI can be used for other high traffic queries e.g. /get-by-gender",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
